      <title>🚀 Chinese AI Startup MiniMax Drops New Models to Rival Industry Giants 🤖</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/chinese-ai-company-minimax-models/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/chinese-ai-company-minimax-models/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🌏 Chinese AI companies are flexing their muscles again, and MiniMax just threw down the gauntlet with &lt;em&gt;three&lt;/em&gt; new AI models! 💥 Backed by Alibaba 🛍️ and Tencent 🎮, MiniMax has raised a cool $850 million 💰 and is valued at over $2.5 billion. That&amp;rsquo;s enough dough to buy every avocado toast in Silicon Valley 🥑🍞.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here’s the tea 🍵:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-models-&#34;&gt;The Models 🚀&lt;a href=&#34;#the-models-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-minimax-text-01&#34;&gt;1️⃣ MiniMax-Text-01&lt;a href=&#34;#1-minimax-text-01&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🧠 &lt;strong&gt;Size&lt;/strong&gt;: A brain-busting &lt;strong&gt;456 billion parameters&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;📚 &lt;strong&gt;Skill&lt;/strong&gt;: Outsmarting Google’s Gemini 2.0 Flash 🌟 on math and trivia benchmarks like MMLU and SimpleQA.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🧐 &lt;strong&gt;Context Window&lt;/strong&gt;: A jaw-dropping &lt;strong&gt;4 million tokens&lt;/strong&gt;! That&amp;rsquo;s like reading &lt;em&gt;War and Peace&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;five times&lt;/strong&gt; in one go 📚📚📚📚📚. Meanwhile, GPT-4o is over here squinting at its puny 31x smaller window. 🤏📖&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-minimax-vl-01&#34;&gt;2️⃣ MiniMax-VL-01&lt;a href=&#34;#2-minimax-vl-01&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;👀🤓 &lt;strong&gt;Modality&lt;/strong&gt;: A jack-of-all-trades that can read both text and images.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;📝 &lt;strong&gt;Skill&lt;/strong&gt;: Answers graph-related questions like “What&amp;rsquo;s the peak of the orange line?” with ease on tests like ChartQA.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;⚖️ &lt;strong&gt;Competition&lt;/strong&gt;: Good, but not quite beating OpenAI’s GPT-4o or the open-source InternVL2.5. Nice try though, MiniMax. ✋&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-t2a-01-hd&#34;&gt;3️⃣ T2A-01-HD&lt;a href=&#34;#3-t2a-01-hd&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🎤 &lt;strong&gt;Talent&lt;/strong&gt;: Generates hyper-realistic voices in &lt;strong&gt;17 languages&lt;/strong&gt; and can clone your BFF’s voice from just &lt;strong&gt;10 seconds&lt;/strong&gt; of audio 😱👂.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🎶 &lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: Adjustable cadence, tone, and tenor. No benchmarks here, but it’s reportedly “on par” with Meta and PlayAI’s models. So… 🎵🥂?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;open-but-not-really-open-&#34;&gt;Open but Not Really Open 🛠️🔒&lt;a href=&#34;#open-but-not-really-open-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;MiniMax dropped the models on GitHub 🐙 and Hugging Face 🧸💻, but they’re not entirely “open source.”&lt;/p&gt;</description>
